{"tid":176060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於朱經緯被捕，有D嘢想問？","createTime":"2017-03-28T02:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T12:19:39.000Z","uid":46420,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31f65973ceb59553e4ea531281680fd231d9ca11","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:39:54.000Z","msg":"其有無人諗過？<br />\n<br />\n律政師係計過條數，出賣一個朱經緯，但可以同時做鳩埋佔中三恥同埋陳淑莊個幾條友，就好似七警二年，換嚟旺角義士三年咁？<br />\n<br />\n如果係嘅話，一條退咗休嘅hea鳩警司，換番又大學教授同埋立法會議員，呢條數政府好撚扺喎<br />\n<br />\n利申：講番先，唔係係度曲線叫大家收聲唔好推朱經緯單嘢，呢條撚樣坐監一定要，係只係想講律政師突然咁順攤，似乎要揾其他人墊底啫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61f10105e28bd19d3e8f66493d8c27afd199187","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"丫，仲有，當日燒山有份自己走去自首，大家等睇吓佢有無事，咪知佢有無投共囉，佢個仔捐咗咁多錢比黑警基金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7f473e64f34753ee499bd0f0dd8c021c7319de","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c3aeecd664915fbb8dae94da115d67ecb95fed","tid":176060,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"好撚醒呀你真係"},{"pid":"9370012060577a1e5b62a837883312334e17e59e","tid":176060,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"咩要「換」?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e749d9c2fe9a085c35e061d2c0041b3e83cabea4","tid":176060,"uid":32132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a2388a80901c6f64af1f119e2f3d66395da3cf2","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩要「換」?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有D港豬真係會諗，你拉得黑一定要拉番D佔中嘅人，咁咪公平囉<br />\n<br />\n另外，律政師又或者政府又可以大條道理話，我無選擇性執法，兩邊都有人被捕，咁確實一定會有D唔睇新聞嘅港豬，聽少少又會似為好公平咁喎，你見cctvv都將兩單新聞連住播就知啦"},{"pid":"f278defbda05bb1869cf74fa13ef5baab2cbc96e","tid":176060,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"真正公民抗命嗰班Day 1已經預咗坐監, 而家只係求仁得仁"},{"pid":"2ab58419caf846280a11aa6cfa08be85e6414196","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:54:42.000Z","msg":"今朝茶記我真係聽到有好多廢老睇完新聞講講：『啱啦，嘅然差佬都拉得，咁緊係要拉番D阻街嘅仆街，咁先公平㗎嘛』<br />\n<br />\n跟住我講咗句：『一個換七個，公乜鳩平呀』<br />\n<br />\n廢老：『咁你阻街個D人多D,就緊係拉多D㗎啦』<br />\n<br />\n最後我講咗句你都on撚9就走，因為知道同佢嘈都嘥氣"},{"pid":"f6be0b2ced57c5d718bd1af88e112d8548168cba","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真正公民抗命嗰班Day 1已經預咗坐監, 而家只係求仁得仁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係當中有立法會議員喎，咁你諗吓，如果一個入咗，其他28個都有去佔中喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a052bac8eda2e8f22fa0189851e279e08f8557c","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真正公民抗命嗰班Day 1已經預咗坐監, 而家只係求仁得仁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係當中有立法會議員喎，咁你諗吓，如果一個入咗，其他28個都有去佔中喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有，而家佢地條罪最高七年喎，立法會議員坐多過三個月就DQ㗎喎，你諗吓有幾撚大獲到時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bd8c2cbf1e606d742b10d145f0b112a60402c2","tid":176060,"uid":42221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"好叻。。計哂數"},{"pid":"dded1931bd39074cbcf31cfa262e1cce5272acea","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:00:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好叻。。計哂數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你覺得係咪我諗多咗定點？"},{"pid":"99f8044014ae152fe4e2cd7e76e6a5d4de8dab6e","tid":176060,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"唔通連登真係要風化新聞先多人討論？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac5aea65d50f0d0d97090f84e2f4a898212ac2f","tid":176060,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今朝茶記我真係聽到有好多廢老睇完新聞講講：『啱啦，嘅然差佬都拉得，咁緊係要拉番D阻街嘅仆街，咁先公平㗎嘛』<br />\n<br />\n跟住我講咗句：『一個換七個，公乜鳩平呀』<br />\n<br />\n廢老：『咁你阻街個D人多D,就緊係拉多D㗎啦』<br />\n<br />\n最後我講咗句你都on撚9就走，因為知道同佢嘈都嘥氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一世都踎喺茶記的人，佢睇到的就係百份報同埋CCTVB"},{"pid":"d350ee3b7149ab961f9eba733e496d4e0d76c738","tid":